                    <span>The title should be "The Techniques of Persuasive Selling - How to Persuade People to Buy What You Sell." "Psychology" is advertised in the title, but it's sizzle with no steak. The "techniqes" are standard selling stuff. It's a quick read.</span>
                  
              
